{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/features.png?t=1731088833\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter__1_.gif?t=1731088833\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/engage.png?t=1731088833\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle hordes of the parasitic Vorid and evolve from a simple thief to a magic-wielding warrior. Learn spells and abilities in a fast-paced combat environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/gorithia_combat.gif?t=1731088833\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the Kingdom of Gorithia</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through expansive zones and diverse biomes where exploration is deeply encouraged and rewarded. Descend into the mysterious Forsaken Depths, embrace the enchanting forests of Myrwood, and ascend the towering peak of Mount Gorimarr in this open, interconnected world.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Master Challenging Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dash, climb and soar your way through perilous obstacles. Complete challenging platforming sections to prove your worth and gain powerful rewards. Discover secret passages and previously locked paths with your new-found abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/customize.png?t=1731088833\" /><br>Collect and equip epic trinkets to enhance your combat prowess. Adapt and forge your unique build with 90 different equippable rings, necklaces, and shards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/quiepemtn-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731088833\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Connect with Enduring Survivors</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet and befriend the resilient survivors of the fallen kingdom. Browse local wares, complete quests, and earn mighty rewards.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Conquer Diverse Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face over 70 different enemies and 25 powerful bosses on your quest to find your kin and restore Gorithia.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/journey.png?t=1731088833\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Glimpse into Gorithia's past through timegates. Meet the legendary heroes of old and defeat ancient bosses to unlock new paths, secrets, items, and lore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/timegate-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731088833\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wield Verruna, the Living Blade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become the master of Verruna, a sentient blade with a thirst for blood. Let the bound souls within the shattered sword guide you through the kingdom, helping you understand Gorithian culture, find hidden secrets, and destroy your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/extras/ezgif.com-effects.gif?t=1731088833\" /> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731088833","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/page.bg.jpg?t=1731088833","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059800/capsul